&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will accomplish:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver personalized, seamless support to all customers across the globe via contact channels, including Phone, Email, SMS, Social Media, and Chat, while maintaining quality and productivity standards according to our success matrix, CXPectations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Thrive in a fast-paced environment by confidently solving customer challenges and providing outstanding service.&lt;/li&gt;
