&lt;li&gt;Autonomously model scenarios and understand impacts of changes to demand, supply, and network assumptions and quickly iterate as product performance develops.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regularly generate and report on key KPIs to Brand and Growth teams while flagging potential roadblocks/considerations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Place purchase orders and regularly interface with external partners to ensure correct lead times, on time production, and product delivery.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure items are accurately set-up across multiple digital channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
