&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be joining a small, high-impact Enterprise Systems team that sits at the center of everything Mammoth Brands runs on — finance, supply chain, commercial operations, and the integrations that tie it all together. We&#39;re 11 people, we cover the full SAP S/4HANA landscape, and we think of ourselves as strategic partners to the business, not a technology order-taking function. We move fast, we hold high standards, and right now we&#39;re in an exciting moment of transformation — leaning into what S/4HANA 2023 on RISE can do, including AI-driven automation and embedded analytics. If you want to build, not just maintain, this is the right team.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The SAP Finance Functional Lead is responsible for delivering and supporting SAP solutions that enable Finance operations. This role partners with business stakeholders to gather requirements, evaluate SAP capabilities, and implement scalable solutions aligned to enterprise standards. The Lead ensures system stability, data integrity, and end-to-end process continuity across SAP Financial modules and integrated commercial processes, including interfaces with SAP and non-SAP systems. Key responsibilities include solution design, configuration, testing support, issue triage and escalation management, and driving continuous process and system improvements. The current system is SAP S4 HANA 2023 on Rise.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will accomplish&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the design, configuration, testing and ongoing support of SAP S/4HANA Finance (FI) modules including General Ledger, Controlling, Accounts Payable, Accounts Receivable, Treasury, Group Reporting and Asset Accounting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate business requirements into scalable SAP solutions while ensuring effective integration with other modules such as CO, MM, SD, PP, and Concur.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage the SAP FI application lifecycle, including enhancements, upgrades, and operational support.&lt;/li&gt;
