&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Here’s what you’ll accomplish:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Together with the Director of Tax, you will serve as a key member of the finance team in developing and implementing a robust tax function and processes&lt;/li&gt;
