&lt;li&gt;Coordinate the tax review and audit process with our external financial statement auditors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with and help to manage our 3rd party tax providers ensuring that all tax related issues are identified, communicated and resolved in a timely manner&lt;/li&gt;
